I try not to buff charmed pets cause if charm breaks at the wrong time if we're in the middle of a fight with something thats taking all the groups attention then if I can't handle my own pet I'm screwed.<br>
<br>
Of course it's kinda funny when the group doesn't listen to me and the wizards go through mana blasting away at this mob that's standing next to me.<br>
<br>
Even after<br>
A Crocodile says &quot; My leader is Eline &quot;<br>
A Crocodile says &quot; My leader is Eline &quot;<br>
Guys. It's my pet. Stop casting spells at it. It's my pet.<br>
<br>
They still zapped it a few times.<br>
